---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-cn">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section class="hero">
				<p class="eyebrow">Dongze's Blog</p>
				<h1>你好，我是 DongZe 👋</h1>
				<p class="intro">我是一名学生开发者，来自重庆。这里记录我在计算机视觉、时间序列与 VibeCoding 方向上的实践与思考。</p>
				<div class="cta-group">
					<a class="btn primary" href="blog/">阅读博客</a>
					<a class="btn" href="about/">了解我</a>
					<a class="btn" href="search/">搜索文章</a>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="focus-grid">
				<article>
					<h2>计算机视觉</h2>
					<p>记录模型理解、实验过程和视觉任务中的工程化落地。</p>
				</article>
				<article>
					<h2>时间序列</h2>
					<p>沉淀预测、特征与评估方法，关注可解释与可复现。</p>
				</article>
				<article>
					<h2>VibeCoding</h2>
					<p>分享 AI 协作开发流、工具链配置和从想法到上线的速度实践。</p>
				</article>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	main {
		max-width: 960px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2.5rem 1rem 3.5rem;
	}

	.hero {
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 18px;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(var(--gray-light), 0.45), rgba(var(--gray-light), 0.2));
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--gray), 0.25);
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin: 0;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0.6rem 0 0.9rem;
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.7rem);
	}

	.intro {
		margin: 0;
		max-width: 52ch;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
	}

	.cta-group {
		display: flex;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		margin-top: 1.4rem;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.58rem 0.95rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--gray), 0.45);
		border-radius: 10px;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.btn.primary {
		background: var(--accent);
		border-color: var(--accent);
		color: white;
	}

	.focus-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 0.9rem;
		margin-top: 1.2rem;
	}

	.focus-grid article {
		padding: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--gray), 0.3);
		border-radius: 12px;
		background: rgba(var(--gray-light), 0.35);
	}

	.focus-grid h2 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
	}

	.focus-grid p {
		margin: 0.6rem 0 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 780px) {
		.focus-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.hero {
			padding: 1.4rem;
		}
	}
</style>
